messages.id:
/{CommandAddSticker} - adds stickers one by one to your collection
/{CommandAddPack} - adds the entire set to your
/{CommandDeleteSticker} at once - removes the sticker from your set one by one
/{CommandDeletePack} - deletes the sticker set from your set
/{CommandReset} - removes all stickers from your set
/{CommandCancel} - undoes the current operation

To view and send stickers from your set, simply type `@{Username}` (and space) in any chat.
